<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dichloromethane"
      id="dichloromethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sat. NH4Cl(aq)"
      id="sat. NH4Cl(aq)"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dichloromethane"
      volume="23 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="1.56 mL"
      stir="True"
      speed="5.0" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="16 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="sat. NH4Cl(aq)"
      through="undefined"
      solvent_volume="80 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="dichloromethane"
      solvent_volume="20 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="40 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="brine"
      through="cartridge_anhydrous MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="40 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="30 °C"
      pressure="98.6583 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="jacketed filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="Prenyl bromide flask"
      type="Flask"
      chemical="Prenyl bormide" />
    <Component
      id="Sodium methoxide flask"
      type="Flask"
      chemical="Sodium methoxide" />
    <Component
      id="Et2O"
      type="Flask"
      chemical="diethyl ether" />
    <Component
      id="flask_argon_bb"
      type="Flask"
      chemical="argon" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="Sodium methoxide"
      id="Sodium methoxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dimethyl malonate"
      id="dimethyl malonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="3,3-dimethylallyl bromide"
      id="3,3-dimethylallyl bromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq NaHCO3-brine"
      id="aq NaHCO3-brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="argon"
      id="argon"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Prenyl bromide"
      id="Prenyl bromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Sodium methoxide"
      volume="all"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      prime_n_times="0"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Add />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dimethyl malonate"
      volume="2.321 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="3 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Prenyl bromide"
      volume="10 mL"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True"
      prime_n_times="0"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Add />
    </Repeat>
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="5 °C"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="water"
      volume="5 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="aq NaHCO3-brine"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="diethyl ether"
      through="MgSO4"
      repeats="3" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="Et2O"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="20 mL"
      through="MgSO4"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="flask_argon_bb"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="50 mL"
      through="MgSO4"
      move_speed="50.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="218 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="tropinone"
      id="tropinone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="l-selectride"
      id="l-selectride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetrahydrofuran"
      id="tetrahydrofuran"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="chcl3"
      id="chcl3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="naoh"
      id="naoh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="h2o2"
      id="h2o2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nahco3"
      id="nahco3"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tropinone"
      mass="1.39 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="70 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="20.0" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="l-selectride"
      volume="13 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="10.0"
      priming_volume="1.5 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="3 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="naoh"
      volume="20 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="h2o2"
      volume="6 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="10.0"
      priming_volume="1.5 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="20 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="60 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="nahco3"
      volume="30 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="phenylacetyltropine flask"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="dma"
      id="dma"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="phenylacetyltropine"
      id="phenylacetyltropine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="formaldehyde"
      id="formaldehyde"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="basic buffer"
      id="basic buffer"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nahco3"
      id="nahco3"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dma"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="basic buffer"
      volume="5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="formaldehyde"
      volume="1.6 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="basic buffer"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="nahco3"
      volume="60 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="2"
      remove_dead_volume="False"
      stir_time="1.5 min"
      settling_time="1.5 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="5"
      remove_dead_volume="False"
      stir_time="1.5 min"
      settling_time="1.5 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="nacl"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2"
      remove_dead_volume="False"
      stir_time="1.5 min"
      settling_time="1.5 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="mgso4"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="20 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="tropine"
      id="tropine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hcl in et2o"
      id="hcl in et2o"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="phenylacetylchloride"
      id="phenylacetylchloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dmf"
      id="dmf"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nahco3"
      id="nahco3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tropine"
      mass="2.82 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="hcl in et2o"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dmf"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min"
      stir_speed="400 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="phenylacetylchloride"
      volume="2.8 mL"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="1.5 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dmf"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"
      time="3 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="nahco3"
      volume="60 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="3"
      remove_dead_volume="False"
      stir_time="2 min"
      settling_time="2 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="4"
      remove_dead_volume="False"
      stir_time="2 min"
      settling_time="2 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="nacl"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="mgso4"
      move_speed="10.0"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="20 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="carbamate flask"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="bromoalkyne flask"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="buffer_flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask2"
      type="buffer_flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="hcl"
      id="hcl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bromoalkyne"
      id="bromoalkyne"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="carbamate"
      id="carbamate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="copper (I) iodide"
      id="copper (I) iodide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="khmds"
      id="khmds"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetrahydrofuran"
      id="tetrahydrofuran"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethylether"
      id="diethylether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl:nh4oh"
      id="nacl:nh4oh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nh4oh"
      id="nh4oh"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="20.0"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="khmds"
      volume="11.5 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="15 min" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="copper (I) iodide"
      mass="1.91 g" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="2 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="bromoalkyne flask"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="8 mL"
      aspiration_speed="20.0"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="bromoalkyne flask"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="all"
      dispense_speed="0.3" />
    <Add
      vessel="bromoalkyne flask"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="5 mL"
      aspiration_speed="20.0"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="bromoalkyne flask"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="all"
      dispense_speed="10.0"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="20 h" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="nacl:nh4oh"
      repeats="4"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="buffer_flask"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="diethylether"
      repeats="2"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="hcl"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="tbuoh flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="estrone"
      id="estrone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tbuoh"
      id="tbuoh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bf3-et2o"
      id="bf3-et2o"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="na2co3"
      id="na2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="estrone"
      mass="1.35 g" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="45 mL"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="bf3-et2o"
      volume="1.9 mL"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="5 mL"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="2 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="nacl"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="mgso4"
      move_speed="10.0"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="SM"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="silica_plug"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="silica" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="(S)-tert-ButylPHOX"
      id="(S)-tert-ButylPHOX"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1 methyl-2-oxo-cyclohexanecarboxylic acid 2-propenyl ester"
      id="1 methyl-2-oxo-cyclohexanecarboxylic acid 2-propenyl ester"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="PdOAc2"
      id="PdOAc2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethylether"
      id="diethylether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tbme"
      id="tbme"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      gas="argon"
      vacuum_pressure="1 mbar" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="PdOAc2"
      mass="11.2 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="(S)-tert-ButylPHOX"
      mass="77.4 mg" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      gas="argon"
      repeats="1"
      after_vacuum_wait_time="15 min"
      vacuum_pressure="1 mbar" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tbme"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="20.0"
      prime_n_times="0" />
    <Async>
      <EvacuateAndRefill />
    </Async>
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="60 °C"
      time="16 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="silica"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="35 °C"
      pressure="350 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="phenylhydrazine"
      id="phenylhydrazine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetoveratrone"
      id="acetoveratrone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="eatons reagent"
      id="eatons reagent"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethanol"
      id="ethanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetic acid"
      id="acetic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="na2co3"
      id="na2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetoveratrone"
      mass="2.7 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="phenylhydrazine"
      volume="1.8 mL"
      viscous="True"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethanol"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetic acid"
      volume="0.3 mL"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethanol"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="70 °C"
      time="3 h"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="55 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="60 °C"
      pressure="20 mbar" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="eatons reagent"
      volume="15 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="60 °C"
      time="48 h"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="na2co3"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="3"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="mgso4"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="30 mL"
      through="mgso4" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2-furanylboronic acid"
      id="2-furanylboronic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="CH2Cl2"
      id="CH2Cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DIPEA"
      id="DIPEA"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="H2O"
      id="H2O"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-Allylbenzylamine"
      id="N-Allylbenzylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="TBTU"
      id="TBTU"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous NaHCO3"
      id="aqueous NaHCO3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cyclohexylamine"
      id="cyclohexylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="glyoxylic acid monohydrate"
      id="glyoxylic acid monohydrate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="2-furanylboronic acid"
      volume="30 mL"
      time="25 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="50 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="CH2Cl2"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="H2O"
      volume="75 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask"
      product_phase="bottom"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="CH2Cl2"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="200 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="450 mbar"
      time="20 min"
      stir_speed="200 RPM"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="CH2Cl2"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir_speed="200 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="100 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="DIPEA"
      volume="16.55 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="TBTU"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="cyclohexylamine"
      volume="10 mL"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="10 min"
      continue_stirring="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="10 min"
      continue_stirring="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="aqueous NaHCO3"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask"
      product_phase="bottom"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="CH2Cl2"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="200 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="699 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor_1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="reactor_2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="flask_argon_bb"
      type="flask"
      chemical="argon" />
    <Component
      id="EtOAc"
      type="flask"
      chemical="ethyl acetate" />
    <Component
      id="KF-Silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="KF-silica" />
    <Component
      id="MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="CuCl"
      id="CuCl"
      role="catalyst" />
    <Reagent
      name="molecular sieves"
      id="molecular sieves"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="imine acetonitrile solution"
      id="imine acetonitrile solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aryl chloride acetonitrile solution"
      id="aryl chloride acetonitrile solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="vinylstannane DCM solution"
      id="vinylstannane DCM solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetonitrile"
      id="acetonitrile"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="TBAF in ACN"
      id="TBAF in ACN"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dichloromethane"
      id="dichloromethane"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Pd(OAc)2"
      id="Pd(OAc)2"
      role="catalyst" />
    <Reagent
      name="NaOAc"
      id="NaOAc"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="anyhydrouse DMF"
      id="anyhydrouse DMF"
      role="solvent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="molecular sieves"
      mass="0.5 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="CuCl"
      mass="50 mg" />
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="120 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="120 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor_1"
      vacuum_pressure="10 mbar" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="imine acetonitrile solution"
      volume="2 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="1 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="aryl chloride acetonitrile solution"
      volume="2 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="1 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="vinylstannane DCM solution"
      volume="4 mL"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="0.5 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="45 °C"
      time="6 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor_1"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor_1"
      to_vessel="reactor_2"
      volume="12 mL"
      through="KF-silica"
      dispense_speed="2.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor_1"
      to_vessel="reactor_2"
      volume="50 mL"
      through="KF-silica"
      dispense_speed="10.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="50 °C"
      time="5 h"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="70 °C"
      pressure="3 mbar" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_2"
      reagent="NaOAc"
      mass="41.4 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_2"
      reagent="Pd(OAc)2"
      mass="11.3 mg" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor_2"
      repeats="5" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_2"
      reagent="anyhydrouse DMF"
      volume="2 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="120 °C"
      time="24 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_2"
      reagent="ethyl acetate"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor_2"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="120 mL" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Separate />
    </Repeat>
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="water"
      volume="20 mL"
      port="bottom" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      solvent_volume="100 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="200 mL"
      from_port="bottom"
      to_port="evaporate"
      through="MgSO4"
      move_speed="1.0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="EtOAc"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="30 mL"
      to_port="evaporate"
      through="MgSO4"
      move_speed="1.0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="flask_argon_bb"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="50 mL"
      to_port="evaporate"
      through="MgSO4"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor1.1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1.2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor4.1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor4.2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor4.3"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor4.4"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="flask_methanol"
      type="flask"
      chemical="methanol" />
    <Component
      id="flask_acid"
      type="flask"
      chemical="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)" />
    <Component
      id="flask_amine"
      type="flask"
      chemical="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      id="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      id="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      id="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      id="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="solvent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      mass="3.62 g"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      mass="3.89 g"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor1.1" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor1.2" />
    <Wait
      time="10 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Wait
      time="10 min" />
    <StopStir
      vessel="reactor1.1" />
    <StopStir
      vessel="reactor1.2" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.1"
      reagent="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      mass="0.997 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.2"
      reagent="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      mass="1.31 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.3"
      reagent="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      mass="0.997 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.4"
      reagent="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      mass="1.31 mg" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.1" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.2" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.3" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.4" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.1"
      to_vessel="reactor4.1"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.1"
      to_vessel="reactor4.2"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"
      to_vessel="reactor4.3"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"
      to_vessel="reactor4.4"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Wait
      time="24 h" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.1"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.2"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.3"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.4"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="celite" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="3,4-dimethoxyphenol"
      id="3,4-dimethoxyphenol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="MeCN"
      id="MeCN"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzyl bromide"
      id="benzyl bromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="potassium carbonate"
      id="potassium carbonate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="MeCN"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="benzyl bromide"
      volume="3.27 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="20 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="81.65 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      through="celite"
      eluting_solvent="MeCN"
      eluting_volume="20 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="30 °C"
      pressure="110.6658 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="303.3331 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1 N phosphoric acid"
      id="1 N phosphoric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="paraformaldehyde"
      id="paraformaldehyde"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="potassium carbonate water solution"
      id="potassium carbonate water solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triethyl phosphonoacetate"
      id="triethyl phosphonoacetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="paraformaldehyde"
      mass="48 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="110 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1 N phosphoric acid"
      volume="4 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="90 °C"
      time="1.5 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="triethyl phosphonoacetate"
      volume="80 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="35 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="potassium carbonate water solution"
      volume="60 mL"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="500 RPM" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="20 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="brine"
      volume="150 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="diethyl ether"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="440 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="TBAF (0.1 M in THF)"
      id="TBAF (0.1 M in THF)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="TBAF (1 M in THF)"
      id="TBAF (1 M in THF)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetophenone (0.4M in THF)"
      id="acetophenone (0.4M in THF)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="trifluoromethylsilane (0.48M in THF)"
      id="trifluoromethylsilane (0.48M in THF)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetophenone (0.4M in THF)"
      volume="10 mL"
      speed="3.0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="trifluoromethylsilane (0.48M in THF)"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      speed="3.0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="TBAF (0.1 M in THF)"
      volume="0.4 mL"
      stir="True"
      speed="3.0" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="TBAF (1 M in THF)"
      volume="4 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

    <Component

    <Reagent
      name="XPhos Pd Gen2"

      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bifunctional MIDA boronate"
      id="bifunctional MIDA boronate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="boronic acid"
      id="boronic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="potassium phosphate"
      id="potassium phosphate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="potassium phosphate"
      mass="0 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="bifunctional MIDA boronate"
      mass="0 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="XPhos Pd Gen2"
      mass="0 mg" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="flask_holding"
      reagent="boronic acid"
      mass="0 mg" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="argon"
      to_vessel="waste_7"
      volume="125 mL" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="flask_holding"
      solvent="THF"
      volume="20 mL" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="flask_holding" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="28 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchVacuum
      vessel="reactor" />
    <SwitchArgon
      vessel="reactor" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="55 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="flask_holding"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="all"
      time="4 h" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="12 h" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor"
      stir_speed="50 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="100 mL"
      aspiration_speed="5.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="249 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Metadata
    description="Heck reaction"
    product_vessel="filter"
    publication="Org. Lett., 2004, Vol. 6, No. 18, 3155-3158" />

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="rotovap"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="ugi_product"
      id="ugi_product"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="palladium catalyst"
      id="palladium catalyst"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="dimethylacetamide"
      id="dimethylacetamide"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
      id="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Prep>
      <ResetHandling
        solvent="dimethylacetamide" />
      <StartPurge
        vessel="filter"
        gas="nitrogen" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="ugi_product"
        amount="1 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="dimethylacetamide"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="150 RPM"
        amount="20 mL" />
      <AddSolid
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="palladium catalyst"
        amount="70 mg" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
        viscous="True"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="150 RPM"
        amount="1.6 mL" />
    </Prep>
    <Reaction>
      <HeatChill
        vessel="filter"
        temp="100 °C"
        time="16 h"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="150 RPM" />
    </Reaction>
    <Workup>
      <Transfer
        from_vessel="filter"
        to_vessel="rotovap"
        volume="all"
        flush_tubing="True" />
      <Evaporate
        vessel="rotovap"
        temp="55 °C"
        pressure="10 mbar"
        stir_speed="130 RPM" />
    </Workup>
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Metadata
    description="Ugi-Heck cascade reaction"
    product_vessel="filter"
    publication="Org. Lett., 2004, Vol. 6, No. 18, 3155-3158" />

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="flask_methanol"
      type="flask"
      chemical="methanol" />
    <Component
      id="flask_acid"
      type="flask"
      chemical="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)" />
    <Component
      id="flask_amine"
      type="flask"
      chemical="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)" />
    <Component
      id="flask_isocyanide"
      type="flask"
      chemical="cyclohexyl isocyanide" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="rotovap"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      id="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      id="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="palladium catalyst"
      id="palladium catalyst"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="dimethylacetamide"
      id="dimethylacetamide"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
      id="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Prep>
      <ResetHandling
        solvent="methanol"
        volume="5 mL" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
        amount="0.84 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
        stir="True"
        amount="6 mL" />
      <Stir
        vessel="filter"
        time="10 min" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
        stir="True"
        amount="6 mL" />
      <Stir
        vessel="filter"
        time="10 min" />
      <Add
        vessel="flask_isocyanide"
        reagent="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
        amount="0.65 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="flask_isocyanide"
        reagent="methanol"
        stir="True"
        amount="8 mL" />
      <Transfer
        from_vessel="flask_isocyanide"
        to_vessel="filter"
        volume="all"
        flush_tubing="True" />
    </Prep>
    <Reaction>
      <Stir
        vessel="filter"
        time="60 s" />
      <Wait
        time="24 h" />
      <Filter
        vessel="filter"
        wait_time="10 min"
        aspiration_speed="10.0"
        stir="False"
        stir_speed="50 RPM" />
      <ResetHandling
        solvent="dimethylacetamide" />
      <StartPurge
        vessel="filter"
        gas="nitrogen" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="dimethylacetamide"
        stir="True"
        amount="20 mL" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="palladium catalyst"
        amount="221 mg" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="N-methyldicyclohexylamine"
        viscous="True"
        stir="True"
        amount="5.14 mL" />
      <HeatChill
        vessel="filter"
        temp="100 °C"
        time="16 h"
        stir="True" />
    </Reaction>
    <Workup>
      <Transfer
        from_vessel="filter"
        to_vessel="rotovap"
        volume="all"
        flush_tubing="True" />
      <Evaporate
        vessel="rotovap"
        temp="55 °C"
        pressure="10 mbar"
        stir_speed="130 RPM" />
    </Workup>
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="Silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="Silica" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pd2(dba)3-CHCl3"
      id="pd2(dba)3-CHCl3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tri-2-furylphosphine"
      id="tri-2-furylphosphine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="iodobenzene solution in THF"
      id="iodobenzene solution in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2-pyridyldimethyl(vinyl)silane solution in THF"
      id="2-pyridyldimethyl(vinyl)silane solution in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triethylamine solution in THF"
      id="triethylamine solution in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="MS3A"
      id="MS3A"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="3-iodothiophene solution in THF"
      id="3-iodothiophene solution in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="MS3A"
      mass="0.1 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pd2(dba)3-CHCl3"
      mass="78.4 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tri-2-furylphosphine"
      mass="35.2 mg" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      vacuum_pressure="10 mbar" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="iodobenzene solution in THF"
      volume="3 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="1 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2-pyridyldimethyl(vinyl)silane solution in THF"
      volume="4 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="0.5 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="triethylamine solution in THF"
      volume="3 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="67 °C"
      time="9 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="Silica"
      move_speed="5.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2M aqueous sodium carbonate"
      id="2M aqueous sodium carbonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aryl halide"
      id="aryl halide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="deionized water"
      id="deionized water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="n-propanol"
      id="n-propanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="palladium acetate"
      id="palladium acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="the aryl boronic acid"
      id="the aryl boronic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triphenylphosphine"
      id="triphenylphosphine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sodium sulfate"
      id="sodium sulfate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="5 % sodium carbonate solution"
      id="5 % sodium carbonate solution"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="aryl halide"
      mass="1 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="the aryl boronic acid"
      mass="0.692 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="n-propanol"
      volume="10 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="15 min" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="palladium acetate"
      mass="3.6 mg"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="triphenylphosphine"
      mass="12.8 mg"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2M aqueous sodium carbonate"
      volume="3.25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="deionized water"
      volume="2 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="60 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="20 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="7 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethyl acetate"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask"
      product_phase="top" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="5 % sodium carbonate solution"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="42 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2 methyl-3-butyn-2-ol"
      id="2 methyl-3-butyn-2-ol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2M HCl"
      id="2M HCl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="CuI"
      id="CuI"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="EtOAc"
      id="EtOAc"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Pd(PPh3)2Cl2"
      id="Pd(PPh3)2Cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aryl iodide A"
      id="aryl iodide A"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. sodium thiosulfate"
      id="aq. sodium thiosulfate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="magnesium sulfate"
      id="magnesium sulfate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2 methyl-3-butyn-2-ol"
      volume="0.6 mL" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="aryl iodide A"
      mass="1 g"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="CuI"
      mass="37 mg"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Pd(PPh3)2Cl2"
      mass="34 mg"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="3 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2M HCl"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="EtOAc"
      volume="15 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="2M HCl"
      solvent_volume="20 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="aq. sodium thiosulfate"
      solvent_volume="20 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="20 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="cartridge"
      solvent_volume="20 mL" />

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="28 % hydrogen peroxide"
      id="28 % hydrogen peroxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetonitrile"
      id="acetonitrile"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cis-cyclooctene"
      id="cis-cyclooctene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sodium metabisulphite water solution"
      id="sodium metabisulphite water solution"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="cis-cyclooctene"
      volume="6.86 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="34.1 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetonitrile"
      volume="4.77 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="30 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="28 % hydrogen peroxide"
      volume="5.75 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="0.5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="16 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="brine"
      volume="57 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      solvent_volume="57 mL"
      repeats="4" />
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="sodium metabisulphite water solution"
      volume="28.4 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="separator"
      time="60 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      through="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="278 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="30 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous magnesium sulfate(MgSO4)"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous magnesium sulfate(MgSO4)" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="waste_X"
      type="ChemputerWaste" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-dibromoethane and diethyl malonate"
      id="1,2-dibromoethane and diethyl malonate"
      role="reagent" />

      name="50 % aqueous NaOH solution"
      id="50 % aqueous NaOH solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"

      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent

    <Reagent

    <Reagent
      name="toluene"

      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="50 % aqueous NaOH solution"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />

      vessel="filter"

      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />

      vessel="filter"

      volume="7.13 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />

      vessel="filter"
      temp="65 °C"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="30 °C"
      time="40 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="15 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="concentrated hydrochloric acid"
      volume="65 mL"
      stir="True"
      dispense_speed="3.0" />

      stir="True"

    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="brine"
      volume="80 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="500 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="water"
      volume="15 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_magnesium_sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1 M potassium hydrogen sulfate"
      id="1 M potassium hydrogen sulfate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="t-butoxycarbonyl anhydride"
      id="t-butoxycarbonyl anhydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triethylamine methanol solution"
      id="triethylamine methanol solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="magnesium sulfate"
      id="magnesium sulfate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="triethylamine methanol solution"
      volume="30 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="t-butoxycarbonyl anhydride"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM"
      speed="10.0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="24 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="218 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="ethyl acetate"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="1 M potassium hydrogen sulfate"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      through="ethyl acetate"
      solvent_volume="25 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="200 mL"
      through="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="150 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="waste_4"
      type="ChemputerWaste" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="anhydrous tert-butyl alcohol"
      id="anhydrous tert-butyl alcohol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether"
      id="ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pivaloyl chloride"
      id="pivaloyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="trifluoromethanesulfonic acid"
      id="trifluoromethanesulfonic acid"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Dry
      vessel="filter"
      time="30 min"
      temp="120 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="pivaloyl chloride"
      volume="20.25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="anhydrous tert-butyl alcohol"
      volume="3.864 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="85 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="trifluoromethanesulfonic acid"
      volume="7.208 mL"
      time="3 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="100 °C"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="-10 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ether"
      volume="65 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="waste_4"
      volume="500 mL" />
    <Dry
      vessel="filter"
      time="2 min" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <HeatChill />
      <Transfer />
      <Dry />
    </Repeat>
    <Dry
      vessel="filter" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor_1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor_2"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="ZnCl2"
      id="ZnCl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="p-Benzoquinone in DCE"
      id="p-Benzoquinone in DCE"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetoacetate"
      id="ethyl acetoacetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-Methylamine in EtOH"
      id="N-Methylamine in EtOH"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethanol"
      id="ethanol"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-dichloroethane"
      id="1,2-dichloroethane"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="ethanol" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="ethyl acetoacetate"
      volume="4.424 mL"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="1 mL" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="ethanol" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor_1"
      reagent="N-Methylamine in EtOH"
      volume="6.467 mL"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0"
      priming_volume="1 mL" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="ethanol" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor_1"
      time="3 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor_1"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="ethanol"
      rinsing_volume="20 mL"
      rinsing_repeats="3" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="1,2-dichloroethane" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="80 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="1,2-dichloroethane" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor_2"
      reagent="ZnCl2"
      mass="0.905 g" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor_2"
      temp="55 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
