<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="allylamine"
      id="allylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous 1M HCl solution"
      id="aqueous 1M HCl solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dichloromethane"
      id="dichloromethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methyl chloroformate dichloromethane solution"
      id="methyl chloroformate dichloromethane solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous NaCl solution"
      id="saturated aqueous NaCl solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      id="saturated aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="allylamine"
      volume="14 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dichloromethane"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methyl chloroformate dichloromethane solution"
      volume="37 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="18 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dichloromethane"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dichloromethane"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="aqueous 1M HCl solution"
      solvent_volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="saturated aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      solvent_volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="saturated aqueous NaCl solution"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="21.3315 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask1"
      type="buffer_flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask2"
      type="buffer_flask" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1-octyne"
      id="1-octyne"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-Bromosuccinimide"
      id="N-Bromosuccinimide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="a saturated sodium thiosulfate solution"
      id="a saturated sodium thiosulfate solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pentanes"
      id="pentanes"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated NaCl solution"
      id="saturated NaCl solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="silver nitrate"
      id="silver nitrate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1-octyne"
      mass="5 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetone"
      volume="107 mL" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="N-Bromosuccinimide"
      mass="8.8 g"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="silver nitrate"
      mass="0.77 g"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="22 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pentanes"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pentanes"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask1"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="a saturated sodium thiosulfate solution"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask1"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="pentanes"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask1"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated NaCl solution"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      pressure="21.3315 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="diallyl pimelate"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="buffer_flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask2"
      type="buffer_flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="sodium hydride"
      id="sodium hydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetrahydrofuran"
      id="tetrahydrofuran"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="argon"
      id="argon"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="sodium hydride"
      mass="0.396 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="2 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="45 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="24 h" />
    <Confirm
      msg="Add iodomethane (0.73 mL)" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="24 h" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="40.0" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="10 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <StopStir
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="200 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="acetone"
      temp="20 °C"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="etoac"
      solvent_volume="20 mL"
      repeats="3"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="nacl" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="150 mL"
      through="mgso4"
      aspiration_speed="40.0"
      move_speed="10.0" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="20 mL"
      through="mgso4"
      aspiration_speed="40.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="jacketed_filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="MgSO4_sand"
      type="cartridge" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask_1"
      type="vessel" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask_2"
      type="vessel" />
    <Component
      id="ethyl_benzoate_N-vinylpyrrolidin-2-one_mixture flask"
      type="vessel" />
    <Component
      id="toluene flask"
      type="vessel" />
    <Component
      id="anhydrous_THF flask"
      type="vessel" />
    <Component
      id="THF flask"
      type="vessel" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="sodium hydride"
      id="sodium hydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl_benzoate_N-vinylpyrrolidin-2-one_mixture"
      id="ethyl_benzoate_N-vinylpyrrolidin-2-one_mixture"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="anhydrous_THF"
      id="anhydrous_THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated_aqueous_ammonium_chloride"
      id="saturated_aqueous_ammonium_chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="toluene"
      id="toluene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <CSwitchArgon
      pneumatic_controller="Schlenk"
      port="5"
      pressure="low" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      reagent="sodium hydride"
      mass="2.5 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      reagent="anhydrous_THF"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Async>
      <Purge />
    </Async>
    <Async>
      <HeatChill />
    </Async>
    <Add
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      reagent="ethyl_benzoate_N-vinylpyrrolidin-2-one_mixture"
      volume="11.2 mL"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="500 RPM"
      port="top"
      aspiration_speed="5.0" />
    <Wait
      time="10 h" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      reagent="saturated_aqueous_ammonium_chloride"
      volume="30 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="500 RPM" />
    <Stir
      vessel="jacketed_filter"
      time="5 min"
      stir_speed="500 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="jacketed_filter"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="200 mL"
      aspiration_speed="20.0"
      dispense_speed="50.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask_2"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated_aqueous_ammonium_chloride"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask_1"
      settling_time="10 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="buffer_flask_1"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask_2"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="toluene"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="2"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask_1"
      settling_time="10 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask_2"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="250 mL"
      through="MgSO4_sand" />
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="toluene"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="250 mL"
      through="MgSO4_sand" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="30 °C"
      pressure="1 mbar"
      time="30 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Metadata
    description="Calix[8]arene synthesis"
    product_vessel="filter"
    publication="Org. Synth. 1990, 68, 243" />

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="flask_chloroform"
      type="flask"
      chemical="chloroform" />
    <Component
      id="flask_xylene"
      type="flask"
      chemical="xylene" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask1"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask2"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="flask_nitrogen"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="tert-butylphenol"
      id="tert-butylphenol"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="paraformaldehyde"
      id="paraformaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="sodium hydroxide"
      id="sodium hydroxide"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="xylene"
      id="xylene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="chloroform"
      id="chloroform"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Prep>
      <ResetHandling
        solvent="xylene" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="tert-butylphenol"
        amount="5 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="paraformaldehyde"
        amount="1.5 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="xylene"
        stir="True"
        amount="50 mL" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="sodium hydroxide"
        amount="40 mg" />
    </Prep>
    <Reaction>
      <HeatChill
        vessel="reactor"
        temp="140 °C"
        time="5 h"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="450 RPM" />
      <HeatChillToTemp
        vessel="reactor"
        temp="30 °C"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="150 RPM"
        upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
        lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
      <Wait
        time="15 min" />
    </Reaction>
    <Workup>
      <StartStir
        vessel="reactor"
        stir_speed="300 RPM" />
      <Transfer
        stir_from_vessel="True"
        from_vessel="reactor"
        to_vessel="filter"
        volume="80 mL"
        to_port="top"
        flush_tubing="True"
        rinsing_solvent="xylene"
        rinsing_volume="7 mL"
        rinsing_repeats="2" />
      <StopStir
        vessel="reactor" />
      <Filter
        vessel="filter"
        wait_time="5 min"
        stir="False"
        filtrate_vessel="buffer_flask2" />
    </Workup>
    <Purification>
      <CConnect
        from_vessel="flask_nitrogen"
        to_vessel="filter"
        to_port="bottom" />
      <Add
        vessel="filter"
        reagent="chloroform"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="150 RPM"
        amount="40 mL" />
      <HeatChill
        vessel="filter"
        temp="60 °C"
        time="50 min"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="100 RPM" />
      <HeatChillToTemp
        vessel="filter"
        temp="10 °C"
        stir="False"
        upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
        lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
      <Wait
        time="30 min" />
      <Filter
        vessel="filter"
        wait_time="5 min"
        stir="False"
        filtrate_vessel="buffer_flask1" />
      <Dry
        vessel="filter"
        time="10 min" />
    </Purification>
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="(R)-(+)-2-pyrrolidone-5-carboxylic acid"
      id="(R)-(+)-2-pyrrolidone-5-carboxylic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous,saturated sodium carbonate"
      id="aqueous,saturated sodium carbonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous,saturated sodium chloride solution"
      id="aqueous,saturated sodium chloride solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dichloromethane"
      id="dichloromethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="thionyl chloride"
      id="thionyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="(R)-(+)-2-pyrrolidone-5-carboxylic acid"
      mass="6.6 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="200 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="thionyl chloride"
      volume="0.5 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="24 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="aqueous,saturated sodium carbonate"
      volume="8 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="218 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="dichloromethane"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="aqueous,saturated sodium chloride solution"
      through="anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="10 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="218 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Metadata
    description="Calix[8]arene de-ter-butylation reaction"
    product_vessel="filter"
    publication="Chem. Commun., 2019, 55, 7199-7202" />

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="flask_nitrogen"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="flask_toluene"
      type="flask"
      chemical="toluene" />
    <Component
      id="flask_acid"
      type="flask"
      chemical="HCl" />
    <Component
      id="flask_methanol"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="calixarene"
      id="calixarene"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="AlCl3"
      id="AlCl3"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="phenol"
      id="phenol"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="toluene"
      id="toluene"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="HCl"
      id="HCl"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Prep>
      <ResetHandling
        solvent="toluene" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="calixarene"
        amount="1 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="phenol"
        amount="0.65 g" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="toluene"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="220 RPM"
        amount="40 mL" />
      <Stir
        vessel="reactor"
        time="5 min"
        stir_speed="320 RPM" />
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="AlCl3"
        amount="1.23 g" />
    </Prep>
    <Reaction>
      <HeatChill
        vessel="reactor"
        temp="60 °C"
        time="5 h"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="450 RPM" />
      <HeatChillToTemp
        vessel="reactor"
        temp="30 °C"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="350 RPM"
        upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
        lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    </Reaction>
    <Workup>
      <Add
        vessel="reactor"
        reagent="HCl"
        stir="True"
        stir_speed="420 RPM"
        amount="35 mL" />
      <Stir
        vessel="reactor"
        time="45 min"
        stir_speed="500 RPM" />
      <Transfer
        stir_from_vessel="True"
        from_vessel="reactor"
        to_vessel="rotavap"
        volume="90 mL"
        flush_tubing="True"
        rinsing_solvent="toluene"
        rinsing_volume="4 mL"
        rinsing_repeats="2" />
      <Evaporate
        vessel="rotavap"
        temp="55 °C"
        pressure="63 mbar"
        time="30 min" />
      <Add
        vessel="rotavap"
        reagent="methanol"
        amount="50 mL" />
      <Evaporate
        vessel="rotavap"
        temp="66 °C"
        pressure="1000 mbar"
        stir_speed="200 RPM" />
      <Transfer
        stir_from_vessel="True"
        from_vessel="rotavap"
        to_vessel="filter"
        volume="80 mL"
        to_port="top"
        flush_tubing="True"
        rinsing_solvent="methanol"
        rinsing_volume="7 mL"
        rinsing_repeats="2" />
      <Filter
        vessel="filter"
        wait_time="5 min"
        stir="False"
        filtrate_vessel="buffer_flask" />
      <Dry
        vessel="filter"
        time="10 min" />
    </Workup>
  </Procedure>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="L-(+)-Tartaric acid"
      id="L-(+)-Tartaric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="deionized water"
      id="deionized water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="glacial acetic acid"
      id="glacial acetic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="racemic trans-1,2-diaminocyclohexane"
      id="racemic trans-1,2-diaminocyclohexane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="deionized water"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="racemic trans-1,2-diaminocyclohexane"
      volume="24 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="glacial acetic acid"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="20 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="4 h" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="5 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="60 min" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="water"
      volume="20 mL"
      temp="5 °C"
      vacuum_time="30 s"
      repeats="4" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="methanol"
      volume="20 mL"
      vacuum_time="30 s"
      repeats="4" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="methanol"
      volume="20 mL"
      vacuum_time="30 s"
      repeats="4" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="methanol"
      volume="20 mL"
      vacuum_time="30 s"
      repeats="4" />
    <Dry
      vessel="filter"
      temp="42.5 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

    <Add

    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous potassium carbonate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous potassium carbonate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="waste_X"
      type="ChemputerWaste" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      id="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dry dichloromethane solution of pyridine base"
      id="dry dichloromethane solution of pyridine base"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dry dichloromethane solution of cholest-4-en-3-one"
      id="dry dichloromethane solution of cholest-4-en-3-one"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dry dichloromethane"
      id="dry dichloromethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="trifluoromethanesulfonic anhydride"
      id="trifluoromethanesulfonic anhydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor"
      time="30 min"
      temp="120 °C" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="2 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry dichloromethane solution of pyridine base"
      volume="40 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="trifluoromethanesulfonic anhydride"
      volume="3.32 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry dichloromethane"
      volume="3.3 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry dichloromethane solution of cholest-4-en-3-one"
      volume="40 mL"
      time="17.5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry dichloromethane"
      volume="3.3 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry dichloromethane"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="699 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="waste_X"
      volume="125 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="waste_X"
      volume="125 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="waste_X"
      volume="125 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="anhydrous potassium carbonate"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="699 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="flask_argon_2"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      id="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DMF"
      id="DMF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="formic acid DMF solution"
      id="formic acid DMF solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated sodium bicarbonate solution"
      id="saturated sodium bicarbonate solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tributylamine"
      id="tributylamine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tributylamine"
      volume="3.61 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DMF"
      volume="7.75 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="flask_argon_2"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="400 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="formic acid DMF solution"
      volume="2.58 mL"
      time="2.5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="60 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="diethyl ether"
      solvent_volume="75 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="2 N hydrochloric acid"
      solvent_volume="62 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated sodium bicarbonate solution"
      solvent_volume="62 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="bi-2-naphthol"
      id="bi-2-naphthol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="phosphorus oxychloride"
      id="phosphorus oxychloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="6 N hydrochloric acid"
      id="6 N hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="bi-2-naphthol"
      mass="10 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="45 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="phosphorus oxychloride"
      volume="4.9 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="90 °C"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="55 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="4 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="filter"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="6 N hydrochloric acid"
      volume="90 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      dispense_speed="3.0" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="6 N hydrochloric acid"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="5 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="108 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="water"
      volume="20 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Dry
      vessel="filter" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="Ph3PO"
      id="Ph3PO"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nicotinamide"
      id="nicotinamide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="anhydrous acetonitrile"
      id="anhydrous acetonitrile"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triethylamine"
      id="triethylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="oxalyl chloride"
      id="oxalyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Ph3PO"
      mass="56.8 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="nicotinamide"
      mass="2.493 g" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="anhydrous acetonitrile"
      volume="80 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir_speed="250 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="triethylamine"
      volume="8.448 mL"
      stir="True"
      aspiration_speed="2.0" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="oxalyl chloride"
      volume="3.504 mL"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      to_port="evaporate"
      rinsing_solvent="anhydrous acetonitrile"
      rinsing_volume="20 mL"
      rinsing_repeats="3"
      rinse_withdrawal_excess="5.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="Jones_reagent flask"
      type="flask"
      chemical="Jones_reagent" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask1"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask2"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="CrO3"
      id="CrO3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Jones_reagent"
      id="Jones_reagent"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="H2SO4"
      id="H2SO4"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="HCl"
      id="HCl"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="lithocholic acid"
      id="lithocholic acid"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      reagent="CrO3"
      mass="3.03 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="lithocholic acid"
      mass="0.535 g" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="acetone" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="water" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      solvent="water"
      volume="9 mL"
      time="5 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      reagent="H2SO4"
      volume="2.967 mL"
      viscous="True"
      dropwise="True"
      stir="True" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="acetone" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="acetone"
      volume="50 mL"
      time="5 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="4 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Jones_reagent"
      volume="5 mL"
      dropwise="True"
      stir="True" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="acetone" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="4 °C"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True"
      purpose="reaction" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="5">
      <Add />
      <HeatChill />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="45 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="45 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="water"
      temp="24 °C"
      dry="False"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="acetone"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="separator"
      reagent="HCl"
      volume="5 mL" />
    <SeparatePhases
      separation_vessel="separator"
      lower_phase_vessel="buffer_flask1"
      upper_phase_vessel="buffer_flask2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask1"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="250 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="diethyl ether"
      solvent_volume="25 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="buffer_flask2"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="300 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="20 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="45 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="1.5 h"
      temp="75 °C"
      pressure="5 mbar" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      solvent="water"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      solvent="acetone"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="Jones_reagent flask"
      solvent="water"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="100 mL"
      repeats="1" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="water"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="100 mL"
      repeats="1" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="acetone"
      temp="24 °C"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="acetone" />
    <ResetHandling
      solvent="methanol" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="5 Methylisoxazole"
      id="5 Methylisoxazole"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="CH2Cl2"
      id="CH2Cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="NaOMe"
      id="NaOMe"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="anhyd Et2O (99 %)"
      id="anhyd Et2O (99 %)"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="5 Methylisoxazole"
      volume="1 mL" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="CH2Cl2"
      volume="14 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="NaOMe"
      volume="2.2 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="18 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="16 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="699 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="anhyd Et2O (99 %)"
      volume="20 mL" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="methoxypyridine in THF"
      id="methoxypyridine in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="piperidine in THF"
      id="piperidine in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="LiI"
      id="LiI"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="NaH"
      id="NaH"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="140 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="LiI"
      mass="2.704 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="NaH"
      mass="2 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      vacuum_pressure="10 mbar" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="3.7 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methoxypyridine in THF"
      volume="5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="piperidine in THF"
      volume="5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="75 °C"
      time="8 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="50 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DCM"
      volume="20 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DCM"
      volume="30 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="699 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pd2dba3"
      id="pd2dba3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="phosphine ligand 1"
      id="phosphine ligand 1"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="XPhos"
      id="XPhos"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="5-bromopyrimidine"
      id="5-bromopyrimidine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-aminobenzotrifluoride"
      id="4-aminobenzotrifluoride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="K3PO4"
      id="K3PO4"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="toluene"
      id="toluene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pd2dba3"
      mass="93 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="XPhos"
      mass="0.193 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="K3PO4"
      mass="1.501 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="5-bromopyrimidine"
      mass="0.803 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="4-aminobenzotrifluoride"
      mass="0.987 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      vacuum_pressure="10 mbar" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="toluene"
      volume="10 mL"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="110 °C"
      time="15 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="50 mL"
      through="Celite" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

    <StartStir

    <Transfer

      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.1"
      to_vessel="reactor4.2"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"
      to_vessel="reactor4.3"
      volume="24 mL"

    <Transfer

    <Wait

  </Procedure>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor1.1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1.2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor4.1"

    <Component

    <Component

    <Component
      id="reactor4.4"

      type="flask"
      chemical="methanol" />
    <Component
      id="flask_acid"
      type="flask"
      chemical="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)" />
    <Component
      id="flask_amine"
      type="flask"
      chemical="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      id="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      id="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      role="reagent"
      solid="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      id="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      id="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      id="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="solvent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="4-nitrobenzaldehyde"
      mass="3.62 g"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="4-chlorobenzaldehyde"
      mass="3.89 g"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="allylamine methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor1.1" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor1.2" />
    <Wait
      time="10 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.1"
      reagent="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1.2"
      reagent="2-iodobenzoic acid methanol solution (1 M)"
      volume="24 mL" />
    <Wait
      time="10 min" />
    <StopStir
      vessel="reactor1.1" />
    <StopStir
      vessel="reactor1.2" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.1"
      reagent="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      mass="0.997 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.2"
      reagent="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      mass="1.31 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.3"
      reagent="tert-butyl isocyanide"
      mass="0.997 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor4.4"
      reagent="cyclohexyl isocyanide"
      mass="1.31 mg" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.1" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.2" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.3" />
    <StartStir
      vessel="reactor4.4" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.1"
      to_vessel="reactor4.1"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.1"
      to_vessel="reactor4.2"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"
      to_vessel="reactor4.3"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"
      to_vessel="reactor4.4"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Wait
      time="24 h" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.1"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.2"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.3"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Filter
      vessel="reactor4.4"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

    <StartStir

    <Transfer

      to_vessel="reactor4.2"
      volume="24 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1.2"

    <Transfer

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component

      name="phenylhydrazine"

      role="reagent" />

      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="phenylhydrazine"
      volume="2.95 mL"
      viscous="True"
      priming_volume="2 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"

      stir="True"
      priming_volume="0" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="allyl alcohol"
      id="allyl alcohol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nacl"
      id="nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pTSA"
      id="pTSA"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pimelic acid"
      id="pimelic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nahco3"
      id="nahco3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="toluene"
      id="toluene"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pimelic acid"
      mass="6.4 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pTSA"
      mass="38 mg"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="toluene"
      volume="40 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="allyl alcohol"
      volume="8.2 mL"
      stir="True"
      priming_volume="1.5 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="115 °C"
      time="16 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Transfer />
      <Add />
    </Repeat>
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="nahco3"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="nacl"
      repeats="2" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="150 mL"
      through="mgso4"
      move_speed="10.0"
      dispense_speed="10.0" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="20 mbar"
      time="1.5 h"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

      type="cartridge"

  <Reagents>

    <Reagent

      role="reagent" />

    <Reagent

    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="hcl"
      volume="10 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="SM"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="2 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="SM"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="7 mL"
      dispense_speed="0.05" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="SM"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="1 mL"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"

      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="naoh"
      volume="5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <Add />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      through="mgso4"
      repeats="3"
      remove_dead_volume="False" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="30 mL"
      through="mgso4" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="150 mbar"
      time="45 min" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous Na2SO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous Na2SO4" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="CCl4"
      id="CCl4"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DMF"
      id="DMF"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="PPh3"
      id="PPh3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzyl alcohol"
      id="benzyl alcohol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether"
      id="ether"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sodium azide"
      id="sodium azide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="benzyl alcohol"
      volume="2.08 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="sodium azide"
      mass="1.56 g"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="PPh3"
      mass="11 g"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="CCl4"
      volume="2 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DMF"
      volume="8 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="90 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="10 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ether"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="filter"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="25 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      through="anhydrous Na2SO4" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="Boc-L-leucine hydrate"
      id="Boc-L-leucine hydrate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N,O-dimethylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      id="N,O-dimethylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-Methylpiperidine"
      id="N-Methylpiperidine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous 0.2 N hydrochloric acid"
      id="aqueous 0.2 N hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous 0.5 N sodium hydroxide"
      id="aqueous 0.5 N sodium hydroxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methyl chloroformate"
      id="methyl chloroformate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methylene chloride"
      id="methylene chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      id="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetrahydrofuran"
      id="tetrahydrofuran"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="N,O-dimethylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      mass="39.1 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methylene chloride"
      volume="236 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="2 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="N-Methylpiperidine"
      volume="48.8 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="Boc-L-leucine hydrate"
      mass="100 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="tetrahydrofuran"
      volume="458 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="methylene chloride"
      volume="1.8 l"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="-20 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="N-Methylpiperidine"
      volume="48.8 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="-12 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="methyl chloroformate"
      volume="31 mL"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor2"
      time="2 min" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="reactor2"
      volume="all" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="reactor2" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor2"
      time="4 h" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="5 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="aqueous 0.2 N hydrochloric acid"
      solvent_volume="500 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="aqueous 0.5 N sodium hydroxide"
      solvent_volume="500 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      through="magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="500 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="32.5 °C"
      pressure="350 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor3"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="glass wool"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="glass wool" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="anhydrous AlCl3"
      id="anhydrous AlCl3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="p-TsCl"
      id="p-TsCl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bis(trimethylsilyl)acetylene"
      id="bis(trimethylsilyl)acetylene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="20 % HCl"
      id="20 % HCl"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Async
      pid="dry_reactor">
      <Dry />
      <EvacuateAndRefill />
      <HeatChillToTemp />
    </Async>
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor2"
      time="30 min"
      temp="120 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor2" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="anhydrous AlCl3"
      mass="29.4 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="DCM"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="p-TsCl"
      mass="41.9 g" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Await
      pid="dry_reactor" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="bis(trimethylsilyl)acetylene"
      mass="34 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DCM"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="250 mL"
      through="glass wool"
      time="60 min"
      rinsing_solvent="DCM"
      rinsing_volume="50 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="12 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="-2 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor3"
      reagent="water"
      volume="200 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor3"
      reagent="20 % HCl"
      volume="200 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor3"
      temp="-2 °C"
      time="15 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      stir_to_vessel="True"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="reactor3"
      volume="450 mL"
      time="30 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor3"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="150 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="reactor"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C"
      pressure="10 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="6.2mM aqueous K2CO3/KHCO3"
      id="6.2mM aqueous K2CO3/KHCO3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="chloroform"
      id="chloroform"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="p-tolyl 2-(trimethylsilyl)ethynyl sulfone"
      id="p-tolyl 2-(trimethylsilyl)ethynyl sulfone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="p-tolyl 2-(trimethylsilyl)ethynyl sulfone"
      mass="25.2 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="300 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="6.2mM aqueous K2CO3/KHCO3"
      volume="350 mL"
      time="3.5 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="chloroform"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="4" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="brine"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="197 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pd(xanthos)cl2"
      id="pd(xanthos)cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="(E)-3-phenylprop-2-en-1-ol"
      id="(E)-3-phenylprop-2-en-1-ol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="i-proh"
      id="i-proh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dibenzylamine"
      id="dibenzylamine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pd(xanthos)cl2"
      mass="0.945 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="i-proh"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="60 s" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="(E)-3-phenylprop-2-en-1-ol"
      mass="3.35 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dibenzylamine"
      volume="4.8 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="19 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="i-proh"
      rinsing_volume="20 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="30 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="mcpba"
      id="mcpba"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2-iodotoluene"
      id="2-iodotoluene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-tertbutylbenzene"
      id="4-tertbutylbenzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tfoh"
      id="tfoh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et2o"
      id="et2o"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="mcpba"
      mass="2.46 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="2-iodotoluene"
      volume="1.27 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="4-tertbutylbenzene"
      volume="1.7 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="tfoh"
      volume="1.77 mL"
      dropwise="True"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="60 min" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="filter"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="et2o"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="-10 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="False" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="et2o"
      volume="25 mL"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir_speed="100 RPM" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="celecoxib"
      id="celecoxib"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="k2co3"
      id="k2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bode catalyst 3"
      id="bode catalyst 3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzaldehyde"
      id="benzaldehyde"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethanol"
      id="ethanol"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzylbromide"
      id="benzylbromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dmf"
      id="dmf"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="heptane"
      id="heptane"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="celecoxib"
      mass="2.33 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="k2co3"
      mass="1.69 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="bode catalyst 3"
      mass="32.3 mg" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ethanol"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="filter" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="benzaldehyde"
      volume="0.75 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="70 °C"
      time="16 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="dmf"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="benzylbromide"
      volume="1.09 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="3 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="water"
      volume="100 mL"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="60 min" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="water"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir_speed="100 RPM"
      repeats="2" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="heptane"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir_speed="100 RPM"
      repeats="2" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>
