<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="(diacetoxyiodo)benzene"
      id="(diacetoxyiodo)benzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="mecn"
      id="mecn"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="trifluoroacetic acid"
      id="trifluoroacetic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methyl 4-hydroxyphenylacetate"
      id="methyl 4-hydroxyphenylacetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="toluene"
      id="toluene"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="(diacetoxyiodo)benzene"
      mass="8.72 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="methyl 4-hydroxyphenylacetate"
      mass="3.32 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="mecn"
      volume="150 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Purge
      vessel="reactor1" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="trifluoroacetic acid"
      volume="2.34 mL"
      time="3 min"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="560 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="mecn"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      to_vessel="reactor1"
      volume="all"
      time="3 h"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="32 °C"
      pressure="175 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <Evaporate />
    </Repeat>
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="buffer_flask"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="sodium hydride"
      id="sodium hydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="petroleum ether"
      id="petroleum ether"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="(3-Methyl-2-butenyl)propanedioic acid dimethyl ester"
      id="(3-Methyl-2-butenyl)propanedioic acid dimethyl ester"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="propargyl bromide 80% in toluene"
      id="propargyl bromide 80% in toluene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether"
      id="ether"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="sodium hydride"
      mass="9 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="petroleum ether"
      volume="20 mL"
      repeats="3"
      dry_under_vacuum="False" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="500 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="(3-Methyl-2-butenyl)propanedioic acid dimethyl ester"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True"
      amount="36.4 g" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="propargyl bromide 80% in toluene"
      volume="22 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="16 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="50 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="ether"
      volume="500 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir_speed="150 RPM" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="water" />
    <CleanVessel
      vessel="rotavap"
      solvent="acetone" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="300 mL"
      repeats="3"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="buffer_flask" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="buffer_flask"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="ether"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="150 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="Celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="Celite" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="AIBN"
      id="AIBN"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="(Z)-3-Tributylstannylmethylene-4-isopropyl-1,1-cyclopentanedicarboxylic acid, dimethyl ester"
      id="(Z)-3-Tributylstannylmethylene-4-isopropyl-1,1-cyclopentanedicarboxylic acid, dimethyl ester"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tributyltin hydride"
      id="tributyltin hydride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="silica"
      id="silica"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="AIBN"
      mass="40 mg" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="(Z)-3-Tributylstannylmethylene-4-isopropyl-1,1-cyclopentanedicarboxylic acid, dimethyl ester"
      mass="23.8 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="tributyltin hydride"
      volume="27.9 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="80 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="reactor"
      solvent="DCM"
      volume="1000 mL"
      time="5 min" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="silica"
      mass="350 g" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="48 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      from_port="bottom"
      through="Celite" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="8">
      <Add />
      <Stir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

  <Hardware>

    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="mgcl2"
      id="mgcl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="paraformaldehyde"
      id="paraformaldehyde"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="thf"
      id="thf"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et3n"
      id="et3n"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2-bromophenol"
      id="2-bromophenol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et2o"
      id="et2o"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1m hcl"
      id="1m hcl"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="mgcl2"
      mass="4.76 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="paraformaldehyde"
      mass="2.25 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="thf"
      volume="125 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="et3n"
      volume="6.96 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2-bromophenol"
      volume="2.65 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="75 °C"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="et2o"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="1m hcl"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      through="mgso4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="silica" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pd2dba3-chcl3"
      id="pd2dba3-chcl3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="agco3"
      id="agco3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1-iodo-4-fluorobenzene"
      id="1-iodo-4-fluorobenzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzothiophene"
      id="benzothiophene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hfip"
      id="hfip"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pd2dba3-chcl3"
      mass="0.194 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="agco3"
      mass="1.55 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="benzothiophene"
      mass="1.01 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1-iodo-4-fluorobenzene"
      volume="1.3 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="hfip"
      volume="15 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="16 h" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="3">
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="4-phenyl-1-butene"
      id="4-phenyl-1-butene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="p-iodoanisole"
      id="p-iodoanisole"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="t-butyliodide"
      id="t-butyliodide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dioxane"
      id="dioxane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="nibr2-glyme"
      id="nibr2-glyme"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dtbbpy"
      id="dtbbpy"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. nh4cl"
      id="aq. nh4cl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. nacl"
      id="aq. nacl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="nibr2-glyme"
      mass="0.154 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dtbbpy"
      mass="0.161 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="p-iodoanisole"
      mass="4.68 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dioxane"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="5 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="t-butyliodide"
      volume="3.58 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="4-phenyl-1-butene"
      volume="1.5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="16 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="etoac"
      volume="250 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="aq. nh4cl"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="aq. nacl"
      through="mgso4"
      solvent_volume="40 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="silica" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="6-bromobenzothiophene"
      id="6-bromobenzothiophene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="csf"
      id="csf"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pd(pph3)4"
      id="pd(pph3)4"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetyltrimethylsilane"
      id="acetyltrimethylsilane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dce"
      id="dce"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="heptane"
      id="heptane"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="6-bromobenzothiophene"
      mass="2 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="csf"
      mass="5.7 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pd(pph3)4"
      mass="0.543 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetyltrimethylsilane"
      volume="2.7 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dce"
      volume="10 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="75 °C"
      time="24 h"
      stir="True"
      stir_speed="800 RPM" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="heptane"
      volume="20 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="silica"
      flush_tubing="True"
      rinsing_solvent="etoac"
      rinsing_volume="60 mL"
      rinsing_repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="31 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="MgSO4_cartridge"
      type="cartridge" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="N-Cyclopentylbenzamide"
      id="N-Cyclopentylbenzamide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2-iodopyridine"
      id="2-iodopyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-dichloroethane"
      id="1,2-dichloroethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Tf2O"
      id="Tf2O"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1-Phenyl-1-propyne"
      id="1-Phenyl-1-propyne"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      id="aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="N-Cyclopentylbenzamide"
      mass="0.1135 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2-iodopyridine"
      volume="63.8 ul" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1,2-dichloroethane"
      volume="3 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Tf2O"
      volume="0.1007 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="15 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1-Phenyl-1-propyne"
      volume="25 ul"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="90 °C"
      time="18 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="aqueous NaHCO3 solution"
      volume="3 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="60 min" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="celite" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pyrazole"
      id="pyrazole"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="CuBr"
      id="CuBr"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="GalA"
      id="GalA"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="K2CO3"
      id="K2CO3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="50 % aqueous DMSO"
      id="50 % aqueous DMSO"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="bromobenzene"
      id="bromobenzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="EtOAc"
      id="EtOAc"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent"
      use_for_cleaning="True" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="bromobenzene"
      volume="3.35 mL" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyrazole"
      mass="2.71 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="CuBr"
      mass="0.23 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="GalA"
      mass="0.678 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="K2CO3"
      mass="13.2 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="50 % aqueous DMSO"
      volume="80 mL" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="100 °C"
      time="24 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="EtOAc"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      through="celite"
      eluting_solvent="EtOAc"
      eluting_volume="100 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="100 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_cotton"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="cotton" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl 2-(ethoxymethylene)malonate"
      id="diethyl 2-(ethoxymethylene)malonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="K2CO3"
      id="K2CO3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aniline"
      id="aniline"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="EtOAc"
      id="EtOAc"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      id="methylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methylhydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      mass="51.2 mg" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="diethyl 2-(ethoxymethylene)malonate"
      volume="0.125 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="8.2 ul" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="85 °C"
      time="4 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="aniline"
      volume="46.5 ul"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="K2CO3"
      mass="69.1 mg"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="EtOAc"
      volume="3 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="6 h" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      through="cotton"
      eluting_solvent="EtOAc" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_Na2SO4_silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="Na2SO4/silica" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="acetophenone"
      id="acetophenone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="urea"
      id="urea"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sulfur"
      id="sulfur"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DMSO"
      id="DMSO"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethyl acetate"
      id="ethyl acetate"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="5% aqueous NaHCO3"
      id="5% aqueous NaHCO3"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetophenone"
      mass="1.2 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="urea"
      mass="1.8 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="sulfur"
      mass="0.5 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="DMSO"
      volume="10 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="120 °C"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="2.5 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="120 °C"
      time="2.5 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethyl acetate"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="5% aqueous NaHCO3"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="brine"
      through="Na2SO4/silica"
      solvent_volume="10 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="silica" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1"
      type="reactor1" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor1" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="benzyl azide"
      id="benzyl azide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dce"
      id="dce"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="phenylacetylene"
      id="phenylacetylene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cp*rucl(cod)"
      id="cp*rucl(cod)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="cp*rucl(cod)"
      mass="0.285 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="benzyl azide"
      mass="1.71 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor2" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor1" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="dce"
      volume="150 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="phenylacetylene"
      volume="8.66 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="45 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Wait
      time="5 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="dce"
      volume="5 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      to_vessel="reactor1"
      volume="all"
      flush_tubing="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="45 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="35 °C"
      pressure="40 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="silica"
      rinsing_solvent="etoac"
      rinsing_volume="50 mL"
      rinsing_repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="35 °C"
      pressure="40 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="Grubbs I"
      id="Grubbs I"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="n-boc-diallylamine"
      id="n-boc-diallylamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetrakis(hydroxymethyl)phosphonium sulfate"
      id="tetrakis(hydroxymethyl)phosphonium sulfate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="naoh"
      id="naoh"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et3n"
      id="et3n"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="Grubbs I"
      mass="0.146 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="90 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="n-boc-diallylamine"
      volume="7.66 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="2.5 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="tetrakis(hydroxymethyl)phosphonium sulfate"
      volume="8.6 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="5 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="70 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="naoh"
      mass="0.62 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="8 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor2"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      to_vessel="reactor1"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="methanol"
      rinsing_volume="5 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="et3n"
      volume="50 ul"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor1"
      time="16 h"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="water"
      volume="80 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor1"
      time="10 min"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="40 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="brine"
      through="mgso4"
      solvent_volume="40 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pd(ch3cn)2cl2"
      id="pd(ch3cn)2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="xantphos"
      id="xantphos"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzene"
      id="benzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et2o"
      id="et2o"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="pd(ch3cn)2cl2"
      mass="1 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="xantphos"
      mass="2.46 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="filter" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="benzene"
      volume="80 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="110 °C"
      time="48 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="20 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="benzene"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir_speed="100 RPM"
      repeats="3" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="et2o"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir_speed="100 RPM"
      repeats="3" />
    <Dry
      vessel="filter"
      time="5 h" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous sodium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous sodium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      id="aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethylene dichloride"
      id="ethylene dichloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanesulfonic acid"
      id="methanesulfonic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methylene chloride"
      id="methylene chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="b'b-dibromoisobutyric acid"
      id="b'b-dibromoisobutyric acid"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="b'b-dibromoisobutyric acid"
      mass="61.5 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="31 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethylene dichloride"
      volume="75 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methanesulfonic acid"
      volume="0.2 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="95 °C"
      time="24 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methylene chloride"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      through="anhydrous sodium sulfate" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="30 °C"
      pressure="140 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="celite" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="solution"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="anhydrous benzene"
      id="anhydrous benzene"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methyl dibromoisobutyrate"
      id="methyl dibromoisobutyrate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="triethylamine"
      id="triethylamine"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="methyl dibromoisobutyrate"
      mass="20 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="anhydrous benzene"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="solution"
      reagent="triethylamine"
      volume="10.6 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="solution"
      reagent="anhydrous benzene"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      stir_to_vessel="True"
      stir_speed="600.0"
      from_vessel="solution"
      to_vessel="reactor"
      volume="all"
      time="1.5 h" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="80.1 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="20 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      through="celite"
      eluting_solvent="anhydrous benzene"
      eluting_volume="20 mL"
      eluting_repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="32.5 °C"
      pressure="162 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="solution"
      type="reactor" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether"
      id="ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="l-threitol 1,4-bismethanesulfonate"
      id="l-threitol 1,4-bismethanesulfonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="potassium hydroxide"
      id="potassium hydroxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="solution"
      reagent="potassium hydroxide"
      mass="11.6 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="solution"
      reagent="water"
      volume="35 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="l-threitol 1,4-bismethanesulfonate"
      mass="25 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ether"
      volume="180 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="solution"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      time="15 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="45 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="DCM"
      rinsing_volume="20 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      through="MgSO4"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_MgSO4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="MgSO4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="3M (S,S)-1,2,3,4-diepoxybutane THF solution"
      id="3M (S,S)-1,2,3,4-diepoxybutane THF solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="DCM"
      id="DCM"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="copper iodide"
      id="copper iodide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1M phenylmagnesium bromide THF solution"
      id="1M phenylmagnesium bromide THF solution"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous ammonium chloride"
      id="saturated aqueous ammonium chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether"
      id="ether"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="copper iodide"
      mass="1.89 g" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor"
      repeats="1"
      after_vacuum_wait_time="10 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="-30 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1M phenylmagnesium bromide THF solution"
      volume="99 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="10 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="3M (S,S)-1,2,3,4-diepoxybutane THF solution"
      volume="11 mL"
      time="10 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="2.5 h"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="saturated aqueous ammonium chloride"
      volume="200 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="15 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="separator"
      volume="all" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      through="MgSO4"
      waste_phase_to_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="DCM"
      through="MgSO4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="4" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="350 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      temp="50 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1,4-dioxane"
      id="1,4-dioxane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2,2,2-trifluoro-1 methoxyethanol"
      id="2,2,2-trifluoro-1 methoxyethanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetamide"
      id="acetamide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hexanes/ethyl acetate"
      id="hexanes/ethyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="silica gel"
      id="silica gel"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tert-butyl methyl ether"
      id="tert-butyl methyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="2,2,2-trifluoro-1 methoxyethanol"
      mass="14.75 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="acetamide"
      mass="6 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1,4-dioxane"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="101.1 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="anhydrous magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="EtOH"
      id="EtOH"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="N-(1-chloro-2,2,2-trifluoro-ethyl)acetamide"
      id="N-(1-chloro-2,2,2-trifluoro-ethyl)acetamide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ether/hexanes 7:3"
      id="ether/hexanes 7:3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="potassium O-ethyl xanthate"
      id="potassium O-ethyl xanthate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="N-(1-chloro-2,2,2-trifluoro-ethyl)acetamide"
      mass="9.2 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="EtOH"
      volume="100 mL" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="potassium O-ethyl xanthate"
      mass="9.2 g"
      time="5 min"
      portions="5"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="15 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="water"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="ether/hexanes 7:3"
      through="anhydrous magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="150 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="69.5 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Dry
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="25 °C"
      pressure="1.5 mbar" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-dichloroethane"
      id="1,2-dichloroethane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="lauroyl peroxide"
      id="lauroyl peroxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="vinyl acetate"
      id="vinyl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="S-(1-Acetylamino-2,2,2-trifluoroethyl) O-ethyl dithiocarbonate"
      id="S-(1-Acetylamino-2,2,2-trifluoroethyl) O-ethyl dithiocarbonate"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="S-(1-Acetylamino-2,2,2-trifluoroethyl) O-ethyl dithiocarbonate"
      mass="12.4 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="vinyl acetate"
      volume="5.1 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1,2-dichloroethane"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="83.5 °C"
      time="15 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="4">
      <AddSolid />
      <HeatChill />
    </Repeat>
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="83.5 °C"
      time="45 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="magnesium_sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="aqueous_sodium_hydroxide"
      type="flask" />
    <Component
      id="aqueous_hydrochloric_acid"
      type="flask" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1-hexyne"
      id="1-hexyne"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="5% aqueous sodium hydroxide"
      id="5% aqueous sodium hydroxide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether"
      id="diethyl ether"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hexane"
      id="hexane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="0.5M aqueous hydrochloric acid"
      id="0.5M aqueous hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      id="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="trichloroacetyl chloride"
      id="trichloroacetyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dimethoxyethane"
      id="dimethoxyethane"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="zinc-copper"
      id="zinc-copper"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="zinc-copper"
      mass="39.23 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="diethyl ether"
      volume="400 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="1-hexyne"
      volume="23 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="trichloroacetyl chloride"
      volume="44.6 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dimethoxyethane"
      volume="125 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      stir_to_vessel="True"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      time="60 min" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="18 h" />
    <FilterTo
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="separator" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="hexane"
      volume="200 mL"
      filtrate_vessel="separator" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="aqueous_hydrochloric_acid"
      temp="5 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="aqueous_sodium_hydroxide"
      temp="5 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="0.5M aqueous hydrochloric acid"
      solvent_volume="200 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="5% aqueous sodium hydroxide"
      solvent_volume="200 mL" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="aqueous_hydrochloric_acid" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="aqueous_sodium_hydroxide" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      through="magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="200 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      pressure="200 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_magnesium_sulfate"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="magnesium sulfate" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1 N hydrochloric acid"
      id="1 N hydrochloric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="3-butyl-4,4-dichlorocyclobutenone"
      id="3-butyl-4,4-dichlorocyclobutenone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="diethyl ether/pentane (1:1)"
      id="diethyl ether/pentane (1:1)"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ethanol"
      id="ethanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="glacial acetic acid"
      id="glacial acetic acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      id="saturated aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      id="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tetramethylethylenediamine"
      id="tetramethylethylenediamine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="zinc dust"
      id="zinc dust"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="zinc dust"
      mass="52.6 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="tetramethylethylenediamine"
      volume="121 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ethanol"
      volume="270 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="glacial acetic acid"
      volume="46 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="3-butyl-4,4-dichlorocyclobutenone"
      mass="26.59 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ethanol"
      volume="27 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      stir_to_vessel="True"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="50 mL"
      time="10 min" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="15 min" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="filter" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="2.5 h" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="filter" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter"
      filtrate_vessel="separator" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="diethyl ether/pentane (1:1)"
      volume="1.5 l"
      filtrate_vessel="separator" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="1 N hydrochloric acid"
      solvent_volume="500 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="water"
      solvent_volume="500 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated aqueous sodium bicarbonate"
      solvent_volume="800 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="saturated aqueous sodium chloride"
      through="magnesium sulfate"
      solvent_volume="500 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      pressure="200 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_celite"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="celite" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="4-hydroxy-2-butanone"
      id="4-hydroxy-2-butanone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="benzyl bromide"
      id="benzyl bromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dry toluene"
      id="dry toluene"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="silver oxide"
      id="silver oxide"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="4-hydroxy-2-butanone"
      volume="4.3 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dry toluene"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="silver oxide"
      mass="13.9 g"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="benzyl bromide"
      volume="8.34 mL"
      time="5 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      time="18 h"
      stir="True" />
    <FilterThrough
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      through="celite"
      eluting_solvent="dry toluene"
      eluting_volume="50 mL"
      eluting_repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="48 mbar"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      id="1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="oxalyl chloride"
      id="oxalyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="heptane"
      id="heptane"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2.0M dimethylamine in THF"
      id="2.0M dimethylamine in THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="pyridine"
      id="pyridine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="EtOAc"
      id="EtOAc"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="Et2O"
      id="Et2O"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      mass="50.1 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="Et2O"
      volume="700 mL"
      aspiration_speed="10.0" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="10 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="oxalyl chloride"
      volume="37.1 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="Et2O"
      volume="60 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      time="30 min" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="4 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="heptane"
      volume="400 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="30 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="heptane"
      volume="300 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Dissolve
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="THF"
      volume="500 mL"
      time="2 min" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="2.0M dimethylamine in THF"
      volume="175 mL"
      time="30 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="pyridine"
      volume="46 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="100 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      to_vessel="filter"
      volume="all"
      time="30 min" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="60 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="heptane"
      volume="600 mL" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="water"
      volume="1000 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="30 min" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="EtOAc"
      volume="600 mL"
      time="40 min" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="heptane"
      volume="400 mL"
      time="40 min" />
    <Dry
      vessel="filter"
      time="16 h"
      temp="40 °C" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
    <Component
      id="filtrate_flask"
      type="ChemputerFlask" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="2.3 M LiAlH4 in 2-Me-THF"
      id="2.3 M LiAlH4 in 2-Me-THF"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="THF"
      id="THF"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="3-[2-(dimethylamino)-2-oxoacetyl]-1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      id="3-[2-(dimethylamino)-2-oxoacetyl]-1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="2-Me-THF"
      id="2-Me-THF"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="H2O"
      id="H2O"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="1M aqueous NaOH"
      id="1M aqueous NaOH"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="NH3:MeOH:CH2Cl2 (0.7:9.3:90)"
      id="NH3:MeOH:CH2Cl2 (0.7:9.3:90)"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="3-[2-(dimethylamino)-2-oxoacetyl]-1H-indol-4-yl acetate"
      mass="31.5 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="2-Me-THF"
      volume="1000 mL" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="2.3 M LiAlH4 in 2-Me-THF"
      volume="140 mL" />
    <StopHeatChill
      vessel="filter" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="30 min" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="80 °C"
      time="3 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="filter"
      temp="20 °C"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="1M aqueous NaOH"
      volume="0.15 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="H2O"
      volume="0.15 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="500 mL" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="20 min" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter"
      filtrate_vessel="filtrate_flask" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="NH3:MeOH:CH2Cl2 (0.7:9.3:90)"
      volume="200 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="THF"
      volume="500 mL" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter"
      filtrate_vessel="filtrate_flask" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filtrate_flask"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="pyrollidine"
      id="pyrollidine"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="4-phenylbutyric acid"
      id="4-phenylbutyric acid"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et3n"
      id="et3n"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hobt"
      id="hobt"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="edci-hcl"
      id="edci-hcl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="0.5m hcl"
      id="0.5m hcl"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. nahco3"
      id="aq. nahco3"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="brine"
      id="brine"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="hobt"
      mass="4.05 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="edci-hcl"
      mass="5.75 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="et3n"
      volume="4.17 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="pyrollidine"
      volume="2.48 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="4-phenylbutyric acid"
      mass="4.92 g" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="14 h" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="reactor"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="0.5m hcl" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="separator"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="aq. nahco3" />
    <Separate
      purpose="wash"
      from_vessel="separator"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="brine"
      through="mgso4" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_filter"
      type="cartridge" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="allyl bromide"
      id="allyl bromide"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine-2-thiol"
      id="5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine-2-thiol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="k2co3"
      id="k2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="acetone"
      id="acetone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="mcpba"
      id="mcpba"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. nahco3"
      id="aq. nahco3"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="k2co3"
      mass="2.8 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="5-(trifluoromethyl)pyridine-2-thiol"
      mass="1.79 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="acetone"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="allyl bromide"
      volume="1 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor1"
      time="4 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="cartridge_filter"
      rinsing_solvent="acetone"
      rinsing_volume="25 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="100 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="reactor2"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="ch2cl2"
      rinsing_volume="25 mL" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="mcpba"
      mass="6.2 g" />
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor2"
      time="3 h" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="aq. nahco3"
      volume="60 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      through="mgso4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

</XDL>

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4_2"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor1"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="reactor2"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-diphenylethanone"
      id="1,2-diphenylethanone"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="methanol"
      id="methanol"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      id="hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="sodium acetate"
      id="sodium acetate"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="etoac"
      id="etoac"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ac2o"
      id="ac2o"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="1,2-diphenylethanone"
      mass="5.88 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      mass="2.5 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="sodium acetate"
      mass="3.69 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="methanol"
      volume="50 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="75 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="reactor1"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="150 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="water"
      volume="40 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor1"
      reagent="etoac"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor1"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="top"
      solvent="etoac"
      through="cartridge_mgso4"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="3" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="120 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <StopStir
      vessel="rotavap" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="rotavap"
      to_vessel="reactor2"
      volume="all"
      rinsing_solvent="ch2cl2"
      rinsing_volume="25 mL" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="ac2o"
      volume="5.67 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="50 °C"
      time="2 h"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor2"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"
      stir="True"
      upper_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C"
      lower_temp_tolerance="0.5 °C" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor2"
      reagent="water"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <Separate
      purpose="extract"
      from_vessel="reactor2"
      separation_vessel="separator"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      product_phase="bottom"
      solvent="ch2cl2"
      through="cartridge_mgso4_2"
      solvent_volume="50 mL"
      repeats="2" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      pressure="50 mbar"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>

<?xdl version="2.0.0" ?>
<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_mgso4"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="mgso4" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="separator"
      type="separator" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="1,2-diphenylethanone o-acetyloxime"
      id="1,2-diphenylethanone o-acetyloxime"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="dmf"
      id="dmf"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="cs2co3"
      id="cs2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="10% etoac/hexane"
      id="10% etoac/hexane"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="aq. nacl"
      id="aq. nacl"
      role="reagent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="1,2-diphenylethanone o-acetyloxime"
      mass="4.22 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="cs2co3"
      mass="7.82 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="dmf"
      volume="50 mL" />
    <EvacuateAndRefill
      vessel="reactor" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="80 °C"
      time="60 min"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChillToTemp
      vessel="reactor"
      temp="25 °C"
      active="False"
      continue_heatchill="False"

<XDL>

<Synthesis>

  <Hardware>
    <Component
      id="cartridge_silica"
      type="cartridge"
      chemical="silica" />
    <Component
      id="reactor"
      type="reactor" />
    <Component
      id="rotavap"
      type="rotavap" />
    <Component
      id="filter"
      type="filter" />
  </Hardware>

  <Reagents>
    <Reagent
      name="O-benzyl hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      id="O-benzyl hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="na2co3"
      id="na2co3"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="ch2cl2"
      id="ch2cl2"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="water"
      id="water"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="p-trifluoromethyl benzoyl chloride"
      id="p-trifluoromethyl benzoyl chloride"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="et2o"
      id="et2o"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="tbuocl"
      id="tbuocl"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="hexane"
      id="hexane"
      role="solvent" />
    <Reagent
      name="naopiv"
      id="naopiv"
      role="reagent" />
    <Reagent
      name="mecn"
      id="mecn"
      role="solvent" />
  </Reagents>

  <Procedure>
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="O-benzyl hydroxylamine hydrochloride"
      mass="5.59 g" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="na2co3"
      mass="7.42 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="110 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="water"
      volume="30 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <HeatChill
      vessel="filter"
      temp="0 °C"
      time="20 min"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="p-trifluoromethyl benzoyl chloride"
      volume="5.2 mL"
      dropwise="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="5 h" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="filter"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="et2o"
      volume="60 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Filter
      vessel="filter" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="water"
      volume="20 mL" />
    <WashSolid
      vessel="filter"
      solvent="et2o"
      volume="20 mL"
      vacuum_time="30 min" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="ch2cl2"
      volume="70 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Add
      vessel="filter"
      reagent="tbuocl"
      volume="4.17 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Stir
      vessel="filter"
      time="2 h" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="filter"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <Add
      vessel="rotavap"
      reagent="hexane"
      volume="35 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      time="30 min"
      mode="auto" />
    <AddSolid
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="naopiv"
      mass="4.95 g" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="mecn"
      volume="25 mL"
      stir="True" />
    <Repeat
      repeats="2">
      <Add />
      <StopStir />
      <Transfer />
    </Repeat>
    <Stir
      vessel="reactor"
      time="2 h"
      stir_speed="600 RPM" />
    <Add
      vessel="reactor"
      reagent="et2o"
      volume="75 mL" />
    <Transfer
      from_vessel="reactor"
      to_vessel="rotavap"
      volume="all"
      through="silica"
      rinsing_solvent="et2o"
      rinsing_volume="25 mL" />
    <Evaporate
      vessel="rotavap"
      temp="40 °C"
      mode="auto" />
  </Procedure>

</Synthesis>
